reviews.text: Just an ordinary fast food shop.
Not many seats. Luckily not a very busy branch.
Limited lunch menu, food not well cooked. Value priced menu.

Generic food quality you can expect from the franchise. Their location is away from the busy business area, attracing less people during peak lunch time, which is a good thing. Powerful air conditioning gives welcome refresh during warm and sticky time.
It's always the best for fast food chain of this price level
